<td width="10"><img src="http://www.maximumeq.com/forum/Images/SmallNew.gif" border="0" alt="New Message"></td><td width="50%"><font face="Verdana" size="1" color="EEEEEE"><b>HT vs LH (modified 0 times)</b> </font></td><td width="50%" align="RIGHT"><font face="Verdana" size="1" color="EEEEEE"><b>elementalist</b></font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
